# MemoryCaptures can get excessive in size.
# They all start with the word "Snapshot" and end with ".memsnap".
# Uncomment the next line in order to remove these files from the repository. This may cause the project to not sync optimally with Visual Studio and other IDEs.
#[Mm]emory[Cc]aptures/

# Builds
*.apk
*.aab
*.unitypackage
*.app

